Title: Jenna Lives
Plot: Jenna's big accident is a distant memory, and she actually starts to feel normal again until a strange stalker brings her suicide stigma back to life. Jenna even starts to wonder if her "that girl" reputation is preventing Matty from seeing her as girlfriend material or. does he already have one?
ParentalRatingReason: M Sex scenes and offensive language
GuestStars: Jessica Lu, Mike Faiola, Jillian Murray, Wesam Keesh, Catfish Jean, Angela de Silva, Brennan Murphy, Drake Kemper, Corby Sullivan
